      "text": "当日に、凄い先生からいろいろなダンスを習えるのに\n自分で先に習っちゃう葵さんも葵さんですけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though she could've learned from amazing teachers on the day‚\nAoi-san went and learned them beforehand. That’s so like her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 291.1000071208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 295.1999879204
    },
    {
