      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 299.1000404541
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_02-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "そこはまぁ、葵ならやりかねないけれど……\nそういえば、こころの様子も変じゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ that's something Aoi would do…\nSpeaking of which‚ isn’t Kokoro acting weird too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 299.3333404541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 303.1666545871
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
