      "text": "莉央と愛じゃないか\nあぁ、さっきたまたま廊下でこの先生と知り合ったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ Rio and Ai.\nAh‚ I just happened to meet this teacher in the hallway earlier.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 341.9999745686,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
